Program: Outlook
Title: Orri Vigfusson's Solution to Overfishing
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbqyw
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Icelandic vodka baron Orri Vigfusson is fighting the overfishing of salmon by buying up fishing licences. Also in the programme, homelessness in Bombay; Why do some people find it so difficult to be on time? and a pre-millennium symbolic bonfire in Chicago.